{"type":"text","timestamp":1775840236166,"sessionID":"ses_287ad1f95ffeMyrF2TCi0knVW6","part":{"id":"prt_d78537795001d3VAucRu64BXwA","messageID":"msg_d78536cde0017jAqfsyX9fueBR","sessionID":"ses_287ad1f95ffeMyrF2TCi0knVW6","type":"text","text":"## AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Archive Summary\n\n### Completed\n\n1. **CodeInterpreterSpec 类型定义** (`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go:66-77`)\n   - `Enabled` (bool), `Image` (string), `Resources` (*ResourceQuota)\n   - 作为 `AgentRuntimeSpec` 的嵌套字段 (`types.go:160`)\n\n2. **验证逻辑** (`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/validation.go:171-188`)\n   - `validateCodeInterpreter`: 验证 image 格式和资源配额\n\n3. **CRD Manifest** (`manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml`)\n   - 独立的 CodeInterpreter CRD，包含 `authMode`, `maxSessionDuration`, `sessionTimeout`, `ports`, `template`, `warmPoolSize` 等字段\n   - 支持 status 子资源\n\n4. **RBAC 配置** (`deployment/design.md:107-112`)\n   - workloadmanager ClusterRole 包含 CodeInterpreter 的完整操作权限\n\n### Deferred\n\n1. **独立 CodeInterpreter CRD 类型** — Delta spec 要求的独立 `CodeInterpreter` Kind 未实现为 Go 类型，当前仅作为 Helm chart 的 CRD manifest 存在\n\n2. **CodeInterpreter 生命周期管理** — 未实现独立的执行策略 (`ExecutionPolicy`)、语言选择 (`language`)、代码字段 (`code`) 等运行时执行相关字段\n\n3. **client-go 生成代码** — `client-go/` 目录不存在，未生成typed client/informer/lister\n\n4. **Deepcopy 生成** — `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 未包含 CodeInterpreter 相关方法","time":{"start":1775840236164,"end":1775840236164}}}
